  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the ground pork and cook until browned, breaking it up with a spoon.",
    "Add the bagoong, patis, fish sauce, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the bok choy and green peas. Cook until the bok choy has wilted and the peas are tender.",
    "Season with more patis and fish sauce to taste.",
